channel.description:
[b]I have a big problem,[/b] I want to make a new Home at [u]"Piscatoris Fishing Colony"[/u] [b]Known as the place where you can catch Monkfish.[/b] But i can't get out of the city. i have removed the gate which stays in the wall, but when I go down, i see a fence with a unwalkable floor around it. I have deleted the fence, but the floor won't dismiss. :confused: [b]PLEASE HELP ME! :eek:[/b]
:confused: ???HOW TO DELETE UNWALKABLE FLOORS??? :confused:
